    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did that and we hid in some place which she advised to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, from there you can see me and when I walk then within about a minute, start following.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what we did, we followed her and then we went to her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She lived on the third floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were nothing but high, high-ranking officers living in that house, plus immediately underneath her was the Ukrainian chief of police, the chief of the militia Ukrainian was living underneath her.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And to get into her apartment was another story because to walk up the three flights of stairs not to be noticed or to go and live not to be noticed was another story.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
